Titolo: Off the Wall (1991 video game)

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Off the Wall is an arcade game produced by Atari Games and released in North America in 1991.  A remake of Breakout, it has a much wider variety of gameplay elements of the original. Most notably, it models spin on the ball. Off the Wall supports up to three players simultaneously (though most cabinets only support two). The game's graphics include many backgrounds modeled after modern abstract art.